🌙 Mehwish Chat AI 2.0 – Islamic + Tech Digital Assistant

Powered by Groq LLaMA | Built with FastAPI

✨ Overview

Mehwish Chat AI 2.0 ek multilingual AI digital assistant hai jo Islamic guidance + modern technology solutions ek saath provide karta hai.
Ye project Groq’s LLaMA-3 models par based hai aur specially design kiya gaya hai for:

📖 Islamic Knowledge (Quran & Hadith references)

💻 Technical & Programming Help

🌍 Multilingual Conversations (English, Urdu, Roman Urdu, Arabic)

🎨 AI-powered Image/Media Generation

🚀 Features

🔹 Groq LLaMA 70B integration for ultra-fast inference

🔹 REST API (FastAPI) with ready endpoints

🔹 Frontend support with Jinja2 templates & static files

🔹 Image & Pixel AI API integration

🔹 Cross-platform access (PC + Mobile friendly)

🔹 Clean project structure for easy deployment

📂 Project Structure
Mehwish-Chat-AI-2.0/
│── main.py              # FastAPI entrypoint
│── templates/           # Jinja2 frontend HTML
│── static/              # CSS / JS / Images
│── .env                 # API keys (Groq, Pixels etc.)
│── LICENSE              # MIT License
│── README.md            # Documentation

⚡ Quick Start
# Clone repo
git clone https://github.com/kawish304/Mehwish-Chat-AI-2.0.git
cd Mehwish-Chat-AI-2.0

# Install requirements
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run server
uvicorn main:app --reload


Open in browser: 👉 http://127.0.0.1:8000

